<html>
<head><title>New Data Record Alert</title></head>
<body>
Hi <%= @user.name %>,
<br><br>
You might be interested in a new record that was just added to the <a href="http://threed-staging.heroku.com">Development Data Catalog</a>:
<br><br>
Title: <%= @record.title %><br>
Topics: <%= @record.tag_list.join(', ') %><br>
Geographical Coverage: <%= @record.coverage_list.join(', ') %><br>
<br><br>
Check it out!
<br><br>
Cheers,<br>
Your friends at Data Uncovered
<br><br>
P.s. You received this message because you asked us to notify you when new records are added to the catalog that match the following criteria.
<br><br>
Topics (any): ( <%= @user.alert_topics_list.join(', ') %> )<br>
AND<br>
Geographical Coverages (any): ( <%= @user.alert_locations_list.join(', ') %> )<br>
<br><br>
To change these preferences or to stop receiving notifications, please visit <a href="http://threed-staging.heroku.com/profile/edit">http://threed-staging.heroku.com/profile/edit</a>.
</body></html>
